{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"Transfer Window Simulator","description":"\n**Transfer Window Financial Simulator**\n\nSimulate transfer windows with full FFP impact analysis.\n\n**Access levels:**\n-  **Anonymous / Public** — search clubs, view squads, view FFP dashboards (Capology estimates)\n-  **User** — + save transfer simulations, edit profile\n-  **Sport Director** — + set private real salaries, see accurate FFP calculations\n-  **Admin** — + manage users, force data syncs\n\n**Transfer types:** BUY · SELL · LOAN IN · LOAN OUT (with option-to-buy)\n    ","version":"2.0.0"},"paths":{"/api/v1/auth/register":{"post":{"tags":["Auth"],"summary":"Register","description":"Register a new user. Returns access + refresh tokens immediately.","operationId":"register_api_v1_auth_register_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/RegisterRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"201":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TokenResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/auth/login":{"post":{"tags":["Auth"],"summary":"Login","description":"Login with email + password.","operationId":"login_api_v1_auth_login_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/LoginRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TokenResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/auth/refresh":{"post":{"tags":["Auth"],"summary":"Refresh","description":"Exchange a refresh token for a new access token.","operationId":"refresh_api_v1_auth_refresh_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/RefreshRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TokenResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/auth/me":{"get":{"tags":["Auth"],"summary":"Get Me","description":"Get the authenticated user's profile.","operationId":"get_me_api_v1_auth_me_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/UserResponse"}}}}},"security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}]},"patch":{"tags":["Auth"],"summary":"Update Me","description":"Update own profile (name, username, club affiliation).","operationId":"update_me_api_v1_auth_me_patch","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/UserUpdateRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/UserResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}},"security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}]}},"/api/v1/search/clubs":{"get":{"tags":["Search"],"summary":"Search clubs by name — no auth required","description":"Searches API-Football for clubs matching the query. Results are cached for 6 hours. Use the returned api_football_id to load the full club profile and squad via GET /clubs/{id}.","operationId":"search_clubs_api_v1_search_clubs_get","parameters":[{"name":"q","in":"query","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","minLength":2,"description":"Club name, e.g. 'Manchester' or 'Barcelona'","title":"Q"},"description":"Club name, e.g. 'Manchester' or 'Barcelona'"},{"name":"country","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"string","description":"Optional country filter, e.g. 'England'","default":"","title":"Country"},"description":"Optional country filter, e.g. 'England'"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ClubSearchResult"},"title":"Response Search Clubs Api V1 Search Clubs Get"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/clubs/{api_football_id}":{"get":{"tags":["Clubs"],"summary":"Get club profile — fetches and caches from API-Football if not yet loaded","description":"No auth required. First call fetches from API-Football and syncs squad.","operationId":"get_club_api_v1_clubs__api_football_id__get","parameters":[{"name":"api_football_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Api Football Id"}},{"name":"season","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","default":2024,"title":"Season"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ClubResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/clubs/{api_football_id}/squad":{"get":{"tags":["Clubs"],"summary":"Get club squad — public data for all, salary overrides visible to Sport Directors","description":"Returns all squad players.\n- Regular users / anonymous: Capology salary estimates\n- Sport Directors / Admins: Override salaries shown if set","operationId":"get_squad_api_v1_clubs__api_football_id__squad_get","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"api_football_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Api Football Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/clubs/{api_football_id}/revenue":{"patch":{"tags":["Clubs"],"summary":"Set club annual revenue — Sport Directors / Admins only","description":"Revenue is needed for FFP calculations. Only sport directors with club access can set this.","operationId":"update_revenue_api_v1_clubs__api_football_id__revenue_patch","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"api_football_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Api Football Id"}}],"requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ClubRevenueUpdate"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ClubResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/clubs/{api_football_id}/sync":{"post":{"tags":["Clubs"],"summary":"Force re-sync club squad from API-Football — Sport Directors / Admins only","operationId":"force_sync_api_v1_clubs__api_football_id__sync_post","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"api_football_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Api Football Id"}},{"name":"season","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","default":2024,"title":"Season"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/players/{api_football_id}":{"get":{"tags":["Players"],"summary":"Get player by API-Football ID","description":"Use the `api_football_id` shown in the squad list (e.g. 984, 276).\n\nRegular users see the Capology salary estimate. Sport Directors / Admins also see their private salary override if one is set.","operationId":"get_player_api_v1_players__api_football_id__get","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"api_football_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Api Football Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/players/{api_football_id}/salary-override":{"put":{"tags":["Players"],"summary":"Set real salary — Sport Directors / Admins only","description":"Private. Never shown to regular users. Powers accurate FFP simulations.","operationId":"set_salary_override_api_v1_players__api_football_id__salary_override_put","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"api_football_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Api Football Id"}}],"requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SalaryOverrideRequest"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SalaryOverrideResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}},"delete":{"tags":["Players"],"summary":"Remove salary override — reverts to Capology estimate","operationId":"delete_salary_override_api_v1_players__api_football_id__salary_override_delete","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"api_football_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Api Football Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/simulations/":{"post":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Create a new simulation","description":"Start a simulation for a club + transfer window. Add transfers one by one using the /buys, /sells, /loans-in, /loans-out endpoints below. FFP is recalculated every time you add or remove a transfer.","operationId":"create_simulation_api_v1_simulations__post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationCreateRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"201":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}},"security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}]}},"/api/v1/simulations/my":{"get":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"List my simulations","operationId":"list_my_api_v1_simulations_my_get","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"season","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"e.g. '2025/26'","title":"Season"},"description":"e.g. '2025/26'"},{"name":"window_type","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/WindowType"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Window Type"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationSummary"},"title":"Response List My Api V1 Simulations My Get"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/simulations/{sim_id}":{"get":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Get full simulation — all transfers + FFP projections","operationId":"get_simulation_api_v1_simulations__sim_id__get","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"sim_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Sim Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}},"patch":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Rename simulation or change window/season","operationId":"update_meta_api_v1_simulations__sim_id__patch","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"sim_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Sim Id"}}],"requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/UpdateSimulationMetaRequest"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}},"delete":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Delete a simulation","operationId":"delete_simulation_api_v1_simulations__sim_id__delete","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"sim_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Sim Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/simulations/{sim_id}/buys":{"post":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Add a player purchase","description":"**Sign a new player.** Fee is amortized over the contract length. Full salary added to wage bill.\n\n**To find a player from another club:**\n1. `GET /api/v1/search/clubs?q=Barcelona` → get their `api_football_id`\n2. `GET /api/v1/clubs/{id}/squad` → find the player, copy their `api_football_id`\n3. Use that id as `api_football_player_id` here (optional but links to real data)\n\n**Example — sign Vinicius Jr:**\n```json\n{\n  \"player_name\": \"Vinicius Jr\",\n  \"position\": \"LW\",\n  \"age\": 24,\n  \"transfer_fee\": 150000000,\n  \"annual_salary\": 20000000,\n  \"contract_length_years\": 5,\n  \"api_football_player_id\": 276  \n}\n```","operationId":"add_buy_api_v1_simulations__sim_id__buys_post","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"sim_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Sim Id"}}],"requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/AddBuyRequest"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/simulations/{sim_id}/buys/{index}":{"delete":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Remove a buy by its list index (0-based)","operationId":"remove_buy_api_v1_simulations__sim_id__buys__index__delete","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"sim_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Sim Id"}},{"name":"index","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Index"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/simulations/{sim_id}/sells":{"post":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Add a player sale","description":"**Sell one of your players.** Removes their wages and amortization from your books.\n\n**Tip:** Get your squad from `GET /api/v1/clubs/{api_football_id}/squad`.\nSet `api_football_player_id` so the engine auto-loads their real salary and book value.\n\n**Example — sell Rashford:**\n```json\n{\n  \"player_name\": \"M. Rashford\",\n  \"position\": \"LW\",\n  \"transfer_fee\": 40000000,\n  \"api_football_player_id\": 35845\n}\n```\nIf `api_football_player_id` not set, provide `annual_salary` manually.","operationId":"add_sell_api_v1_simulations__sim_id__sells_post","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"sim_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Sim Id"}}],"requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/AddSellRequest"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/simulations/{sim_id}/sells/{index}":{"delete":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Remove a sell by index","operationId":"remove_sell_api_v1_simulations__sim_id__sells__index__delete","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"sim_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Sim Id"}},{"name":"index","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Index"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/simulations/{sim_id}/loans-in":{"post":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Add a loan-in (take a player on loan)","description":"**Bring a player on loan from another club.**\n\n`wage_contribution_pct` = the % of their salary **your club** pays.\nThe parent club pays the rest.\n\n| Your % | Meaning |\n|--------|---------|\n| 100    | You pay everything (rare) |\n| 50     | Split 50/50 (common) |\n| 30     | You pay 30%, parent pays 70% |\n| 0      | Parent pays everything (rare) |\n\n**Example — loan Zirkzee from Man Utd, you pay 60%:**\n```json\n{\n  \"player_name\": \"J. Zirkzee\",\n  \"position\": \"ST\",\n  \"age\": 23,\n  \"annual_salary\": 5200000,\n  \"wage_contribution_pct\": 60,\n  \"loan_fee\": 3000000,\n  \"contract_length_years\": 1,\n  \"has_option_to_buy\": true,\n  \"option_to_buy_fee\": 35000000,\n  \"option_to_buy_year\": 1\n}\n```","operationId":"add_loan_in_api_v1_simulations__sim_id__loans_in_post","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"sim_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Sim Id"}}],"requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/AddLoanInRequest"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/simulations/{sim_id}/loans-in/{index}":{"delete":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Remove a loan-in by index","operationId":"remove_loan_in_api_v1_simulations__sim_id__loans_in__index__delete","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"sim_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Sim Id"}},{"name":"index","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Index"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/simulations/{sim_id}/loans-out":{"post":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Add a loan-out (send your player on loan)","description":"**Send one of your players out on loan.**\n\n`wage_contribution_pct` = the % of their salary **your club** still pays.\nThe loan club pays the rest.\n\n| Your % | FFP impact |\n|--------|------------|\n| 0      | Fully off your wage bill ✅ |\n| 30     | Still paying 30% (partial relief) |\n| 100    | No wage relief at all ❌ |\n\n**Example — loan out Hannibal, fully off your books:**\n```json\n{\n  \"player_name\": \"Hannibal Mejbri\",\n  \"position\": \"CM\",\n  \"api_football_player_id\": 278166,\n  \"loan_fee_received\": 1000000,\n  \"wage_contribution_pct\": 0\n}\n```","operationId":"add_loan_out_api_v1_simulations__sim_id__loans_out_post","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"sim_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Sim Id"}}],"requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/AddLoanOutRequest"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/simulations/{sim_id}/loans-out/{index}":{"delete":{"tags":["Transfer Simulations"],"summary":"Remove a loan-out by index","operationId":"remove_loan_out_api_v1_simulations__sim_id__loans_out__index__delete","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"sim_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Sim Id"}},{"name":"index","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Index"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SimulationResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/ffp/club/{api_football_id}":{"get":{"tags":["FFP Dashboard"],"summary":"FFP compliance dashboard — real squad + optional simulation overlay","description":"Returns FFP analysis based on the club's **real current squad**.\n\nOptionally pass `?sim_id=<simulation_id>` to overlay a simulation on top —\nthis shows what FFP would look like **if you executed those transfers**.\n\n**What's calculated:**\n- **Squad Cost Ratio** = (wages + amortization) / revenue. UEFA limit: ≤ 70%\n- **Break-Even Result** = 3-year rolling profit/loss. Limit: -€5M (or -€60M with equity)\n- **3-year projection** = forward-looking compliance forecast\n\n**With simulation overlay:**\n- Buys → add wages + amortization to squad cost\n- Sells → remove player wages + amortization\n- Loans in → add % of wages based on `wage_contribution_pct`\n- Loans out → remove % of wages based on `wage_contribution_pct`\n\n`squad_cost_ratio` is a decimal: `0.19` = 19% of revenue.\n\nNo auth required for public data. Sport Directors see salary override calculations.","operationId":"get_ffp_dashboard_api_v1_ffp_club__api_football_id__get","security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}],"parameters":[{"name":"api_football_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","title":"Api Football Id"}},{"name":"sim_id","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Simulation ID to overlay on real squad FFP","title":"Sim Id"},"description":"Simulation ID to overlay on real squad FFP"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/FFPDashboardResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/admin/users":{"get":{"tags":["Admin"],"summary":"List all users","operationId":"list_users_api_v1_admin_users_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/UserResponse"},"type":"array","title":"Response List Users Api V1 Admin Users Get"}}}}},"security":[{"HTTPBearer":[]}